Installation:

  Puzzle: git clone https://psimon@git.puzzle.ch/users/psimon/dotvim ~/.vim
  Private Mirror: git clone https://ps@git.s-it.ch/users/ps/dotvim ~/.vim 

Create symlinks:

  ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
  ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

  cd ~/.vim
  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Upgrade all installed plugins ( git submodules )

git submodule foreach git pull origin master
